text:
Yo Paki!

text:
Yo BHANDari!!

BSBE building -> BSBE Lab -> Chemical Canteen -> Library this sort of became our daily routine back in third year, although all what we did was just cry over every possible thing XD.

Bahut "funnnn" kiya hai BSBE gang mein. I just can't imagine my campus life without you guys, all of you have been such an essential and beautiful part of my college life. 
From getting irritated by the mere presence of a certain someone to maggi in chemical canteen everything was fun with you. Politics se leke bollywood tak har cheez ke baare mein itne discussions kiye hain, itne saare dog videos share kiye hain, itni gossips ki aur sabme bahut maza aya.

Marshy se milna hai yaar :((

Next time jab saath mein video banayenge to pehle se hi practice karke aaunga :(
Thanks for being such an amazing and helpful friend <3
Thodi kam tension liya kar  
PS: Stay hydrated, room pahunch kar text kardena 
Aur.... Bhai hai tu mera
